==Hindi==
===Etymology===
Sanskrit
===Noun===
'''रूप''' (rūpa) {{m}}
# outward [[appearance]], form, figure, shape, appearance, semblance, image, representation, picture
# face, countenance, aspect, features
# colour
# beautiful appearance
# handsome form or figure, shapeliness, beauty, elegance, grace
# natural state or condition, case
# natural disposition, nature, character
# feature, sign, symptom
# kind, sort, species
# mode, manner, method
# (in [[arithmetic]]) discrete quantity, the number one, arithmetical unit; integer number
# (in Hindi poetry) a symbolical expression for one
# the known or absolute number, known quantity
# a drama, play, dramatic composition

===References===
